text: Cecilia Díaz Mesa (born 19 June 1996) is a Cuban water polo player. She was a member of the Cuba women's national water polo team at the 2019 Pan American Games and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * cecilia-diaz-table-of-cuba * cecilia-diaz-mesa-of-cuba-controls- the-ball Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban water polo players
